title: Kalani's Ultimate Djembe Jam Video
description:
In this best-selling DVD, expert instructor Kalami shows you everything you need to know to tune, play, and make music with your djembe. From fundamental techniques shown from multiple angles to traditional rhythms at slow and fast tempos, this DVD has it all.

Special Features
History and Background
Tuning your drum
Getting ready to play
Djembe techniques
Dundun techniques
Jam tracks
Printable notation

Plus
Authentic rhythms. You'll learn: Kassa, Foli, Dansa, and Dununba. Each arrangement features 2 djembe and three dununs parts. That's 20 different rhythm patterns!
